children.name: vaccines
children.choice_filter:
(name = 'bcg' and ${e_bcg} = '') or 
(name = 'opv0' and ${e_opv0} = '') or 
(name = 'penta1' and number(${existing_age}) > 35 and ${e_penta1} = '') or 
(name = 'pcv1' and number(${existing_age}) > 35 and ${e_pcv1} = '') or 
(name = 'opv1' and number(${existing_age}) > 35 and ${e_opv1} = '') or 
(name = 'penta2' and number(${existing_age}) > 63 and ${e_penta2} = '') or 
(name = 'pcv2' and number(${existing_age}) > 63 and ${e_pcv2} = '') or 
(name = 'opv2' and number(${existing_age}) > 63 and ${e_opv2} = '') or 
(name = 'penta3' and number(${existing_age}) > 91 and ${e_penta3} = '') or 
(name = 'pcv3' and number(${existing_age}) > 91 and ${e_pcv3} = '') or 
(name = 'opv3' and number(${existing_age}) > 91 and ${e_opv3} = '') or 
(name = 'ipv' and number(${existing_age}) > 91 and ${e_ipv} = '') or 
(name = 'measles1' and number(${existing_age}) > 250 and ${e_measles1} = '') or 
(name = 'measles2' and number(${existing_age}) > 340 and ${e_measles2} = '')
